com.st.st25sdk.RegisterInterface

  • Packages that use RegisterInterface 
    Package Description
    com.st.st25sdk.type5.st25dv
    Provide API related to ST25DV Family Tags and Dynamic Tags including following main features according to product: Password management Area configuration Configurations with access to Static/Dynamic registers Fast Transfer Mode Extended commands
    com.st.st25sdk.type5.st25dvpwm  
    com.st.st25sdk.type5.st25tv
    Provides classes to handle ST25TV Tags (NFC Forum Type5) from STMicroelectronics.
